the message board contains the following features:

- user registration/login (WIP)
- routing to different links
- user posting message
- storing messages in database
- user viewing messages
- route error handling
- success and error message
- logging for troubleshooting



docker compose up -d --build
docker compose down -v

# to run docker in a different machine
docker tag image_name:latest docker_user/dockerhub_name:latest
docker push docker_user/dockerhub_name:latest

Go to different docker machine
docker pull palendin/repo_name:image_name